posts.title: Morning MAGAthread: Trump Returns to Butler, PA
posts.content:
Good morning, my fellow Patriots! Happy Rally Day! Today is a YUUUUGE rally as President Trump returns to the site of his first attempted assassination: The Butler Farm Show in Butler, PA. The doors are opening right now and President Trump is scheduled to speak at 5 PM Trump/Eastern Time.

Pre-rally feeds are already online:

  • RSBN - Rumble - Gettr - YouTube
  • Real America's Voice / War Room - Rumble

Today's rally already has a different feel to it. Supporters have created one of the largest pre-dawn rally lines in the history of Trump rallies. They are going to have the best time today, folks. There's nothing better than spending the day in a Trump rally line, surrounded by frens, talking about saving America, joking about the liberals, and chanting obscene things about Joe Biden. If you haven't been to a Trump rally, you've got a month left. Don't miss your opportunity.

The rally itself will also be different. The family of Corey Comperatore will be there, because President Trump invited them, but also because Corey gave his life to protect them. President Trump will honor his memory and also recognize David Dutch and James Copenhaver: the two other victims of the failed assassination attempt. Lee Greenwood will be in attendance, so expect a tear-jerking performance of "God Bless the USA".

This is also a somber moment given the devastation which has been wroght by Hurricane Helene and the botched response by the Biden-Harris administration. They spent all the money on illegal migrants. They sent more money overseas. Then they claim there's no money left to help the hurricane victims, and they block independent rescue efforts. Elon Musk will also be on-hand for the rally today. He's been involved with rescue efforts and very vocal about the federal governent's efforts to block their delivery of supplies, including Starlink communications equipment.

Can you feel the 2024 energy yet, Patriots? America's anger with the Biden-Harris administration is reaching a fever pitch. Hurricane Helene couldn't be a clearer case of the incompetency of our federal government. It's so bad that many people think it's intentional. Are the Democrats using the hurricane to reduce Trump voters' access to the polls? They used COVID as an opportunity to flood the country with mail-in ballots, so this isn't unreasonable to ask.

There's only one person who can clean up this mess. That's why there are bullets flying at him. Our favorite President, Donald J. Trump, is the only one with the will and the way to clean up the Washington swamp. When this anger turns into record-breaking votes, he will have a definitive mandate to clean house and actually return control of our government to its rightful owners: the People of the United States of America.

Get excited. Get to a Trump rally. Volunteer for your local elections. Sign up to be a poll watcher. Join the voter registration efforts. Join Trump Force 47. Go door-to-door campaigning. Help other people vote. Join your local school board. Run for office. Support your local MAGA candidate. Do whatever you can to help support this movement. It's critical that we win this election, take our country back, and Make America Great Again!

  • Lee Greenwood at the RNC - God Bless the USA
  • Donald J. Trump & J6 Prison Choir - Justice For All
  • John Kahn - Fighter
  • RightAmerica & Trump - Hold On I'm Coming Remix
  • It's Fun to Say MAGA - MAGA YMCA
